# System Plugin PHP

Namespace root: `HelixUltimate\Framework\` under `src/`.

| Area | Namespace / path |
|------|------------------|
| Theme engine | `Core\HelixUltimate` |
| Helpers / AJAX / media | `Platform\` (`Helper`, `Request`, `Blog`, `Media`) |
| Builders | `Platform\Builders\` |
| com_ajax handlers | `HttpResponse\Response` |
| Cache / document | `System\` |
| Form fields | `src/fields/` only (`JFormFieldHelix*`) |

## Conventions

- Bootstrap via `bootstrap.php` (Composer autoload). Do not reimplement autoloading.
- Plugin entry: `helixultimate.php` (CMSPlugin events). Extend events there; put logic in `src/`.
- New form fields → `src/fields/`. Legacy `fields/` is deprecated — do not add there.
- Params XML → `params/` (e.g. `megamenu.xml`, `blog-options.xml`); load via `Form::addFormPath`.
- Layouts → `layouts/` (cpanel, frontend builder). Constants: `HELIX_LAYOUTS_PATH`, `HELIX_LAYOUT_PATH`.
- Prefer DI / injected services over `Factory::getDbo()` in new code.
- Escape output; use language strings (`Text::_()`), not hard-coded UI copy.

```php
// ✅ Framework usage
use HelixUltimate\Framework\Platform\Helper;
$style = Helper::loadTemplateData();

// ❌ Avoid
$dbo = \JFactory::getDbo();
```
